  schema:name "Mustard greens cultivation" ;
  schema:description "Growing protocol for Tendergreen and related cultivars of *Brassica juncea*, optimized for spring and fall sowing. Extremely rapid bolting in heat; unsuitable for summer cultivation in warm climates. Sow direct; mature in 35–45 days under cool conditions." ;
